  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM4.4.4">
<l>vārārum mulaimaṭavāḷ piṉṉaik kāki vaḷaimaruppiṟ kaṭuñciṉattu vaṉtā ḷārnta</l>
<l>kārārtiṇ viṭaiyaṭarttu vatuvai yāṇṭa karumukilpōl tiruniṟatteṉ kaṇṇar kaṇṭīr</l>
<l>ērārum malarppoḻilkaḷ taḻuvi yeṅku meḻilmatiyaik kāltoṭara viḷaṅku cōti</l>
<l>cīrāru maṇimāṭan tikaḻum nāṅkūrt tirutteṟṟi yampalatteṉ ceṅkaṇ mālē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>My Kaṇṇaṉ, whose divine color is like a dark cloud,</l>
<l rend="indent">who received a bride, having killed</l>
<l>The curved-horned, cruel, enraged, powerful, black bulls</l>
<l rend="indent">which had strong legs, for the sake of the simple lady Piṉṉai</l>
<l rend="indent">with bodice-covered breasts, you see,</l>
<l>Is my bright-eyed Māl in Tirutteṟṟiyampalam in Nāṅkūr</l>
<l rend="indent">where beautiful jeweled mansions shine in glittering light</l>
<l>As the wind pursues the lovely moon everywhere</l>
<l rend="indent">embracing gardens of beautiful flowers.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
